<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Fun Facts</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        .fact-box {
            background: white;
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>🌟 Fun Facts 🌟</h1>

    <div class="fact-box">
        <p>🐙 Octopuses have three hearts.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="fact-box">
        <p>🍯 Honey never spoils and can last for thousands of years.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="fact-box">
        <p>🦒 A giraffe's tongue can be up to 50 cm (20 inches) long.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="fact-box">
        <p>🌍 Earth is the only known planet that supports life.</p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
